Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and FACEY PROPERTY are pleased to be exclusively appointed to lease Noble Business Park.  The development is ideally positioned in the heart of Melbourne and minutes from the Eastlink and Monash Freeway exits and entrances. The high-quality units offer unrivalled business exposure and feature office/warehouse/showrooms specifically designed to suit modern growing businesses.

Development details:
+ Only 7 units remaining
+ Development comprises nine state-of-the-art office/warehouse/showrooms
+ Flexible sizes and layouts from 590sqm* to 787sqm* 
+ Mixed Use Zone allowing a multitude of uses (STP)
+ Business exposure to Princes Highway (43,000* vehicles per day)
+ Full height glazing to provide ample natural light to the showrooms and office suites

Location Details
+ M3 Eastlink 1.1km*
+ M1 Monash Freeway 3.5km*
+ Noble Park Train Station 1.7km*
+ Monash University 8km*

Please contact the exclusively listed agents CBRE or FACEY PROPERTY for further information on the development.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: NOBLE BUSINESS CENTRE PRINCES HIGHWAY FRONTAGE SHOWROOM/OFFICE/WAREHOUSES

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer for lease Unit 3, 500 Princes Hwy, Noble Park. 
 
This property is extremely well located on Princes Hwy, situated just 28km* from the CBD and in proximity to major arterial roads: Monash Freeway (5km*) & Eastlink (3km*).

Property features:
•	Spaces available from 1,925sqm* – 5,155sqm*
•	Fully racked high clearance warehousing with 2,660* pallet spaces available
•	Office space optional (599sqm* available)
•	2 large awnings - 1,274sqm* undercover loading
•	3 loading docks
•	Dangerous goods storage capacity
•	Excellent container access & truck maneuverability
•	Short term lease available
•	Ready to occupy immediately
 
Call now for building plans and to arrange private inspections.

*approx.

Having leased 21-23 Summit Road, Noble Park within 2 weeks of being on-market, we don't expect 17-19 Summit Road to be around for much longer!

Situated within the South-Eastern industrial market just 30km* from the Melbourne CBD, this property provides the ultimate warehousing solution with high cubic capacity and multiple access points. 

Site particulars detailed below:
- High clearance warehouse of 3,440sqm* 
- Office size negotiable
- Total building area of 4,554sqm* 
- Excellent container access with two street crossovers onto Summit Road 
- Four (4) roller shutter doors 
- Ample on site car spaces available

Location benefits include: 
- Princes Highway – 700m 
- Monash Freeway ( M1) – 1.4km 
- Eastlink (M3) – 2.2km 
- Sandown Train Station (Cranbourne/Pakenham Line)- 2km 
- Springvale Road – 2.9km*

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact CBRE’s Lachlan Ferguson, Patrick Noone and Alex Grima. All inspections must be booked in advance.
